item.title: Prayer bpn6468 in Sesotho
item.description: Na O teng ea ka tlosang mathata afe kapa afe haese Molimo feela na? E re: Ho rorisoe Molimo! Ke Eena Molimo! Bohle ke bahlanka ba Hae, ‘me bohle ba tlas’a taolo ea Hae. (Source category: Motlosi oa mathata) (Bahaiprayers.net ID: 6468)
